    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Habitus of Pleciobates herczeki sp. nov. in dorsal view. A. holotype, apterous female; B. paratype, apterous male. Scale bar = 3 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10280557/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10280561>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Photographs of bodies of Pleciobates spp. A–C. P. herczeki sp. nov., holotype, apterous female: A. dorsal view; B. lateral view; C. ventral view. D–E. P. tuberculatus Esaki, 1930, apterous female: D. dorsal view; E. ventral view. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10280561/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10280563>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Morphological features of Pleciobates herczeki sp. nov., apterous female.A. body in dorsal view; B. body in lateral view; C. hind margin of metanotum, lateral view; D. abdominal end, lateral view; E. abdominal end, dorsal view; F. abdominal end, ventral view. Scale bars: A–B= 1 mm; C–F = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10280563/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10280565>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Photographs of bodies of Pleciobates herczeki sp. nov., paratype, apterous male. A. dorsal view; B. ventral view. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10280565/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10280569>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Morphological features of Pleciobates herczeki sp. nov., apterous male. A. pygophore, ventral view; B. proctiger, dorsal view; C. endosoma, lateral view; D. left paramere, lateral view; as = apical sclerite, ds = dorsal sclerite, ls = lateral sclerite, vp = ventral projection, vs = ventral sclerite. Scale bar = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10280569/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10280571>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Pleciobates herczeki sp. nov., live habitus in situ. A. Habitat of P. herczeki sp. nov., a broad stream with rocks submerged in water; B. a group of adults and nymphs resting on rock; C. a nymph and an adult male resting on rock; D. a nymph resting on rock; E. an adult female resting on rock. Images not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10280571/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

